13 WHEREAS, increased advocacy, awareness, research and education may bring improved
14 outcomes for patients in earlier detection and treatment.
15 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
16 express support for increased awareness of stomach cancer and recognize that such
17 awareness may lead to earlier detection for patients.
18 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
19 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the public and the
20 press.
